  "diagram_type": "timeline",
  "code": "---\r\ntitle: Security Incident Response - AtlasMesh Fleet OS\r\n---\r\nsequenceDiagram\r\n    participant VA as Vehicle Agent\r\n    participant ZT as Zero-Trust IAM\r\n    participant SM as Security Monitor\r\n    participant IR as Incident Response\r\n    participant PE as Policy Engine\r\n    participant KS as Key/Secret Management\r\n    participant AL as Audit Log\r\n    participant OC as On-Call Team\r\n    \r\n    Note over VA,OC: Security Incident Detection & Response\r\n    \r\n    %% Anomaly Detection\r\n    VA->>+ZT: AuthenticateRequest(Education_StudentDB)\r\n    ZT->>ZT: Validate certificate and permissions\r\n    ZT->>+SM: LogAuthenticationAttempt(Education_ClassroomService)\r\n    SM->>SM: Analyze authentication patterns\r\n    \r\n    alt Suspicious Activity Detected\r\n        SM->>SM: Correlate with threat intelligence\r\n        SM->>+IR: TriggerSecurityAlert(Education_LMS_Portal)\r\n        IR->>IR: Classify incident severity\r\n        IR->>AL: Log security incident\r\n        \r\n        %% Immediate Response\r\n        alt High Severity Incident\r\n            IR->>+PE: EvaluatePolicy(Education_ClassroomService)\r\n            PE->>PE: Execute emergency security policies\r\n            PE->>AL: Log emergency policy activation\r\n            PE->>-IR: PolicyResult(Education_StudentDB)\r\n            \r\n            IR->>+ZT: RevokeVehicleAccess(Education_GradeSync)\r\n            ZT->>ZT: Revoke all active tokens\r\n            ZT->>AL: Log access revocation\r\n            ZT->>-IR: AccessRevoked(Education_GradeSync)\r\n            \r\n            IR->>+KS: RotateVehicleSecrets(Education_LMS_Portal)\r\n            KS->>KS: Generate new certificates immediately\r\n            KS->>AL: Log emergency secret rotation\r\n            KS->>-IR: SecretsRotated(Education_GradeSync)\r\n            \r\n            IR->>+OC: PageOnCallTeam(Education_LMS_Portal)\r\n            OC->>-IR: IncidentAcknowledged(Education_ContentCDN)\r\n            \r\n        else Medium/Low Severity\r\n            IR->>+PE: EvaluatePolicy(Education_LMS_Portal)\r\n            PE->>-IR: PolicyResult(Education_ContentCDN)\r\n            \r\n            IR->>+SM: EnhanceMonitoring(Education_ContentCDN)\r\n            SM->>-IR: MonitoringEnhanced(Education_LMS_Portal)\r\n            \r\n            IR->>+OC: NotifySecurityTeam(Education_ContentCDN)\r\n            OC->>-IR: NotificationReceived(Education_GradeSync)\r\n        end\r\n        \r\n        %% Investigation & Remediation\r\n        IR->>IR: Begin incident investigation\r\n        IR->>+AL: CollectForensicEvidence(Education_ClassroomService)\r\n        AL->>AL: Generate forensic timeline\r\n        AL->>-IR: ForensicEvidence(Education_GradeSync)\r\n        \r\n        IR->>+VA: RequestDiagnosticData(Education_ClassroomService)\r\n        VA->>VA: Collect detailed system state\r\n        VA->>-IR: DiagnosticData(Education_ContentCDN)\r\n        \r\n        %% Recovery Process\r\n        alt Incident Contained\r\n            IR->>+ZT: RestoreVehicleAccess(Education_ClassroomService)\r\n            ZT->>ZT: Validate new identity\r\n            ZT->>AL: Log access restoration\r\n            ZT->>-IR: AccessRestored(Education_StudentDB)\r\n            \r\n            IR->>+VA: NotifySecurityClearance(Education_StudentDB)\r\n            VA->>VA: Resume normal operations\r\n            VA->>AL: Log security clearance\r\n            VA->>-IR: OperationsResumed(Education_ClassroomService)\r\n            \r\n        else Incident Escalated\r\n            IR->>+OC: EscalateIncident(Education_ClassroomService)\r\n            OC->>OC: Engage security experts\r\n            OC->>-IR: IncidentEscalated(Education_LMS_Portal)\r\n        end\r\n        \r\n        %% Post-Incident Activities\r\n        IR->>IR: Generate incident report\r\n        IR->>+AL: ArchiveIncidentEvidence(Education_ClassroomService)\r\n        AL->>-IR: EvidenceArchived(Education_LMS_Portal)\r\n        \r\n        IR->>+PE: UpdateSecurityPolicies(Education_ContentCDN)\r\n        PE->>PE: Incorporate security improvements\r\n        PE->>AL: Log policy updates\r\n        PE->>-IR: PoliciesUpdated(Education_ContentCDN)\r\n        \r\n    else Normal Activity\r\n        ZT->>-VA: AuthenticationSuccess(Education_StudentDB)\r\n        SM->>-ZT: ActivityLogged(Education_LMS_Portal)\r\n    end\r\n",
